  "detailed_description": "<strong>Find the hidden levels, collect all the coins, or play with friends in Sycamore, a 3D platformer under development based around quick, fast-paced movement where you will race to the end of a level and compete in leaderboard times with players from around the world!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/967e4efef27a8e928db7e29dd4ad486c.poster.avif?t=1749599078\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/967e4efef27a8e928db7e29dd4ad486c.webm?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/967e4efef27a8e928db7e29dd4ad486c.mp4?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>- Responsive platforming controls<br>- Multiple level biomes<br>- Multiplayer<br>- Hidden levels<br>- Minigames<br>- CS-Style Surfing<br>- 3rd and 1st person mode<br>- Coin collector mode<br>- Player customisation<br>- Difficulty scaling<br>- Record leaderboards<br>- Full controller support & accessibility options </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/7bb04be93760bc7d155607166a78a8a7.poster.avif?t=1749599078\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/7bb04be93760bc7d155607166a78a8a7.webm?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/7bb04be93760bc7d155607166a78a8a7.mp4?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Planned</h2><strong><br>- New biomes<br>- New challenges<br>- Minigames<br>- PvP Multiplayer<br>- AND MORE!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/61fcead468c4b6eb97ef7d9edbf3afc5.poster.avif?t=1749599078\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/61fcead468c4b6eb97ef7d9edbf3afc5.webm?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/61fcead468c4b6eb97ef7d9edbf3afc5.mp4?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Community</h2><br><strong>- <br>- Suggest features<br>- Report problems<br>- Find new strategies and challenge other players</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Find the hidden levels, collect all the coins, or play with friends in Sycamore, a 3D platformer under development based around quick, fast-paced movement where you will race to the end of a level and compete in leaderboard times with players from around the world!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/967e4efef27a8e928db7e29dd4ad486c.poster.avif?t=1749599078\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/967e4efef27a8e928db7e29dd4ad486c.webm?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/967e4efef27a8e928db7e29dd4ad486c.mp4?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>- Responsive platforming controls<br>- Multiple level biomes<br>- Multiplayer<br>- Hidden levels<br>- Minigames<br>- CS-Style Surfing<br>- 3rd and 1st person mode<br>- Coin collector mode<br>- Player customisation<br>- Difficulty scaling<br>- Record leaderboards<br>- Full controller support & accessibility options </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/7bb04be93760bc7d155607166a78a8a7.poster.avif?t=1749599078\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/7bb04be93760bc7d155607166a78a8a7.webm?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/7bb04be93760bc7d155607166a78a8a7.mp4?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Planned</h2><strong><br>- New biomes<br>- New challenges<br>- Minigames<br>- PvP Multiplayer<br>- AND MORE!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/61fcead468c4b6eb97ef7d9edbf3afc5.poster.avif?t=1749599078\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/61fcead468c4b6eb97ef7d9edbf3afc5.webm?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1297030/extras/61fcead468c4b6eb97ef7d9edbf3afc5.mp4?t=1749599078\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Community</h2><br><strong>- <br>- Suggest features<br>- Report problems<br>- Find new strategies and challenge other players</strong>",
